---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="BroHafizi | Trainer & Pendakwah Digital Malaysia" description="BroHafizi — Membantu organisasi & komuniti melalui training korporat, teknologi AI, dan dakwah digital yang relevan." canonical="https://brohafizi.com/">

<style is:global>

*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:"DM Sans",sans-serif;background:#f2f0eb;color:#1a1a2e;overflow-x:hidden}
nav{background:#0d1b3e;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:0 5%;height:64px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100}
.nav-brand{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px}
.nav-brand strong{color:#fff;font-size:16px;font-weight:600}
.nav-brand span{color:#6b8dba;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:2px}
.nav-links a{color:#adc5de;font-size:13px;padding:8px 14px;border-radius:4px;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.15s}
.nav-links a:hover{background:#1a2f5e;color:#fff}
.nav-social{display:flex;gap:6px}
.nav-social a{width:30px;height:30px;border:1px solid #1e3060;border-radius:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#6b8dba;text-decoration:none;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;transition:all 0.15s}
.nav-social a:hover{background:#1a2f5e;color:#fff}

/* HERO */
.hero{background:#0d1b3e;padding:80px 5% 56px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hero-inner{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 380px;gap:48px;align-items:center;position:relative;z-index:2}
.hero-deco{position:absolute;right:-60px;top:-60px;width:480px;height:480px;border-radius:50%;border:70px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03);pointer-events:none;z-index:1}
.hero-deco2{position:absolute;right:80px;bottom:-100px;width:240px;height:240px;border-radius:50%;border:40px solid rgba(240,192,64,0.04);pointer-events:none;z-index:1}
.hero-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);color:#8aafc8;font-size:11px;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:20px;letter-spacing:0.8px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:22px}
.hero-badge span{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:#f0c040;display:block;animation:pulse 2s infinite;flex-shrink:0}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0.4}}
.hero h1{font-family:"Playfair Display",serif;font-size:clamp(34px,4.5vw,56px);font-weight:700;color:#fff;line-height:1.12;margin-bottom:18px;letter-spacing:-1.5px}
.hero h1 em{font-style:italic;color:#f0c040}
.hero-desc{font-size:15px;font-weight:300;color:#7a9dba;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:32px}
.hero-btns{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:44px}
.btn-gold{background:#f0c040;color:#0d1b3e;padding:12px 28px;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.15s;display:inline-block}
.btn-gold:hover{background:#e6b530}
.btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:#fff;padding:12px 28px;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);transition:all 0.15s;display:inline-block}
.btn-ghost:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)}
.hero-stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px;padding-top:28px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)}
.stat-n{font-family:"Playfair Display",serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#f0c040;line-height:1}
.stat-l{font-size:11px;color:#5a7a9e;margin-top:4px;letter-spacing:0.3px}

/* PHOTO */
.hero-photo-wrap{position:relative;z-index:2}
.hero-photo-frame{width:100%;border-radius:4px 64px 4px 4px;overflow:hidden;position:relative;aspect-ratio:3/4}
.hero-photo-frame img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:top center;display:block}
.hero-photo-tag{position:absolute;bottom:-20px;left:-20px;background:#060f22;border:1px solid #1a2f5e;padding:14px 18px;border-radius:4px;min-width:170px}
.hero-photo-tag small{display:block;font-size:10px;color:#3a5a7e;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:3px}
.hero-photo-tag strong{font-size:13px;color:#f0c040;font-weight:500}
.hero-tags{position:absolute;top:20px;right:-20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
.hero-tag-pill{background:#060f22;border:1px solid #1a2f5e;padding:5px 11px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;color:#7a9dba;white-space:nowrap}

/* MOBILE PHOTO BLOCK */
.hero-photo-mobile{display:none;margin:28px auto 32px;position:relative;max-width:280px}
.hero-photo-mobile .hero-photo-frame{border-radius:4px 48px 4px 4px}
.hero-photo-mobile .hero-photo-tag{bottom:-14px;left:-10px;padding:10px 14px;min-width:150px}
.hero-photo-mobile .hero-photo-tag small{font-size:9px}
.hero-photo-mobile .hero-photo-tag strong{font-size:12px}

/* STATS BAR */
.stats-bar{background:#060f22;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(6,1fr);border-top:1px solid #0d1b3e}
.sb-item{padding:18px 20px;border-right:1px solid #0d1b3e;text-align:center}
.sb-item:last-child{border:none}
.sb-n{font-family:"Playfair Display",serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#f0c040}
.sb-l{font-size:10px;color:#3a5070;margin-top:3px;letter-spacing:0.3px}

/* SECTIONS */
.section{padding:72px 5%}
.s-label{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2.5px;color:#1a56db;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px}
.s-title{font-family:"Playfair Display",serif;font-size:clamp(24px,3.5vw,38px);font-weight:700;color:#0d1b3e;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-0.5px;margin-bottom:14px}

/* SERVICES */
.services-section{background:#0d1b3e;padding:72px 5%}
.services-header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-end;margin-bottom:36px;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px}
.services-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:#1a2f5e;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.svc{background:#0d1b3e;padding:28px 24px;transition:background 0.15s}
.svc:hover{background:#0a1530}
.svc-n{font-size:10px;color:#3a5070;letter-spacing:1.5px;margin-bottom:16px}
.svc-icon{width:38px;height:38px;background:#1a2f5e;border-radius:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px}
.svc-icon svg{width:18px;height:18px;stroke:#f0c040;fill:none;stroke-width:1.5}
.svc h3{font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#e0eaf8;margin-bottom:8px}
.svc p{font-size:12px;color:#4a6a8e;line-height:1.65}
.svc-cta{display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:center;gap:12px;background:#060f22;cursor:pointer;min-height:180px}
.svc-cta:hover{background:#030a15}
.svc-cta svg{stroke:#f0c040;fill:none}
.svc-cta span{font-size:12px;color:#4a6a8e;text-align:center;line-height:1.6}

/* TESTIMONIALS */
.testi-section{background:#f7f5f0;padding:72px 5%}
.testi-carousel{position:relative;margin-top:44px;overflow:hidden}
.testi-track{display:flex;gap:20px;transition:transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);will-change:transform}
.testi-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid #e8e4dc;border-radius:8px;padding:28px 24px;flex-shrink:0}
.testi-q{font-family:"Playfair Display",serif;font-size:30px;color:#1a56db;line-height:1;margin-bottom:10px}
.testi-text{font-size:14px;color:#555;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:16px;font-style:italic}
.testi-divider{width:28px;height:2px;background:#f0c040;margin-bottom:14px}
.testi-author{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.testi-av{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:50%;background:#e8f0fb;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#1a56db;flex-shrink:0}
.testi-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#0d1b3e;margin-bottom:2px}
.testi-role{font-size:11px;color:#999;line-height:1.4}
.testi-controls{display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:center;margin-top:24px;align-items:center}
.testi-btn{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid #d0cdc5;background:#fff;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all 0.15s;font-size:14px}
.testi-btn:hover{background:#0d1b3e;color:#fff;border-color:#0d1b3e}
.testi-dots{display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center;margin-top:14px;justify-content:center}
.testi-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#d0cdc5;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.25s}
.testi-dot.active{background:#1a56db;width:22px;border-radius:4px}

/* SOCIAL MEDIA */
.social-section{background:#fff;padding:72px 5%}
.social-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:14px;margin-top:40px}
.social-card{border:1px solid #eae7e0;border-radius:8px;padding:20px 18px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.2s;background:#fafafa}
.social-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);border-color:var(--sc,#1a56db);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.07)}
.social-icon{width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}
.social-icon svg{width:24px;height:24px}
.social-info{flex:1;min-width:0}
.social-platform{font-size:11px;color:#aaa;margin-bottom:3px;letter-spacing:0.3px}
.social-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#0d1b3e;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
.social-arrow{font-size:14px;color:#ccc;transition:color 0.2s;flex-shrink:0}
.social-card:hover .social-arrow{color:#0d1b3e}

/* BLOG */
.blog-section{background:#0d1b3e;padding:72px 5%}
.blog-header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-end;margin-bottom:32px;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px}
.blog-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:14px}
.blog-card{background:#0a1530;border:1px solid #1a2f5e;border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;cursor:pointer;transition:border-color 0.15s;text-decoration:none;display:block}
.blog-card:hover{border-color:#378add}
.blog-card-img{height:148px;background:#1a2f5e;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;position:relative}
.blog-card-img svg{width:36px;height:36px;stroke:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);fill:none;stroke-width:1}
.blog-card-img .date{position:absolute;top:10px;left:10px;font-size:10px;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.6);color:#8aafc8;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:20px;letter-spacing:0.3px}
.blog-card-body{padding:16px}
.blog-cats{display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px}
.blog-cat{font-size:10px;background:rgba(26,86,219,0.2);color:#7fa8d4;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:10px}
.blog-cat-gold{background:rgba(240,192,64,0.15);color:#c49a00}
.blog-card h3{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:#c8ddf0;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:7px}
.blog-meta{font-size:10px;color:#2a4060}
.blog-more{margin-top:22px;text-align:center}
.blog-more a{color:#7fa8d4;font-size:13px;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid #1a2f5e;padding:9px 22px;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;transition:all 0.15s}
.blog-more a:hover{background:#1a2f5e;color:#fff}

/* CTA */
.cta-section{background:#f0c040;padding:72px 5%;text-align:center}
.cta-section .s-title{color:#0d1b3e;margin:0 auto 14px;max-width:520px}
.cta-section p{font-size:14px;color:rgba(13,27,62,0.65);max-width:440px;margin:0 auto 28px;line-height:1.7}
.cta-btns{display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.btn-dark{background:#0d1b3e;color:#f0c040;padding:12px 30px;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.15s;display:inline-block}
.btn-dark:hover{background:#060f22}
.btn-outline-dark{background:transparent;color:#0d1b3e;padding:12px 30px;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(13,27,62,0.25);transition:all 0.15s;display:inline-block}
footer{background:#060f22;padding:28px 5%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;border-top:1px solid #0d1b3e}
.footer-brand strong{color:#adc5de;font-size:13px}
.footer-brand span{display:block;font-size:10px;color:#2a4060;margin-top:2px}
.footer-copy{font-size:11px;color:#2a4060}

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media(max-width:900px){.stats-bar{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}
  .hero-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:0}
  .hero-photo-wrap{display:none}
  .hero-photo-mobile{display:block}
  .services-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
  .social-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
  .stats-bar{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
}
@media(max-width:600px){.stats-bar{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
  .nav-links{display:none}
  .hero h1{font-size:32px}
  .hero-btns{flex-direction:column}
  .hero-btns a{text-align:center}
  .hero-stats{gap:12px}
  .stat-n{font-size:22px}
  .services-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .social-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .blog-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .services-header,.blog-header{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start}
  .hero-tags{display:none}
}


.about-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:64px;align-items:center}
@media(max-width:768px){
  .about-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:36px}
  .about-focus-box{order:2}
  .about-text-col{order:1}
}
</style>

<section class="hero" aria-label="Pengenalan BroHafizi">
  <div class="hero-deco"></div>
  <div class="hero-deco2"></div>
  <div class="hero-inner">

    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge"><span></span>Pendakwah Digital &bull; AI Strategist &bull; Trainer</div>
      <h1>Bro Hafizi<br><em>Bukan Ustaz.</em><br>Tapi Berdakwah.</h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">Menggabungkan pengalaman dakwah lapangan, strategi media digital dan teknologi AI untuk membantu organisasi, komuniti dan pendakwah bergerak lebih luas, tersusun dan berimpak.</p>
      <div class="hero-btns">
        <a href="/mengenai-saya" class="btn-gold">Kenali Saya &rarr;</a>
        <a href="/hubungi-saya" class="btn-ghost">Jemput Saya</a>
      </div>

      <!-- MOBILE ONLY PHOTO -->
      <div class="hero-photo-mobile">
        <div class="hero-photo-frame">
          <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Mohammad Hafizi Mohd Radzi" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high">
        </div>
        <div class="hero-photo-tag">
          <small>Founder</small>
          <strong>AINA &mdash; AI NGO Accelerator</strong>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div><div class="stat-n">8+</div><div class="stat-l">Tahun Pengalaman</div></div>
        <div><div class="stat-n">200+</div><div class="stat-l">Sesi Dijalankan</div></div>
        <div><div class="stat-n">50+</div><div class="stat-l">Organisasi</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- DESKTOP ONLY PHOTO -->
    <div class="hero-photo-wrap">
      <div class="hero-photo-frame">
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Mohammad Hafizi Mohd Radzi &mdash; Trainer &amp; Pendakwah Digital">
      </div>
      <div class="hero-photo-tag">
        <small>Founder</small>
        <strong>AINA &mdash; AI NGO Accelerator</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-tags">
        <span class="hero-tag-pill">Pendakwah Digital</span>
        <span class="hero-tag-pill">AI Educator</span>
        <span class="hero-tag-pill">NGO Consultant</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="sb-item"><div class="sb-n">8+</div><div class="sb-l">Tahun Pengalaman</div></div>
  <div class="sb-item"><div class="sb-n">200+</div><div class="sb-l">Program Dijayakan</div></div>
  <div class="sb-item"><div class="sb-n">1000+</div><div class="sb-l">Peserta Dilatih</div></div>
  <div class="sb-item"><div class="sb-n">13+</div><div class="sb-l">Negeri di Malaysia</div></div>
  <div class="sb-item"><div class="sb-n">50+</div><div class="sb-l">Organisasi & Institusi</div></div>
  <div class="sb-item"><div class="sb-n">3+</div><div class="sb-l">Negara Terlibat</div></div>
</div>

<section class="services-section">
  <div class="services-header">
    <div>
      <div class="s-label" style="color:#6b8dba">Apa Yang Saya Tawarkan</div>
      <div class="s-title" style="color:#fff;margin-bottom:0">Kepakaran Utama</div>
    </div>
    <a href="/hubungi-saya" class="btn-gold">Jemput Saya</a>
  </div>
  <div class="services-grid">
    <div class="svc">
      <div class="svc-n">01 &mdash; KORPORAT</div>
      <div class="svc-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Corporate Training</h3>
      <p>Leadership, komunikasi berkesan, teambuilding dan produktiviti untuk persekitaran korporat dan GLC.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="svc">
      <div class="svc-n">02 &mdash; MOTIVASI</div>
      <div class="svc-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3 7h7l-5.5 4 2 7L12 16l-6.5 4 2-7L2 9h7z"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Motivasi &amp; Soft Skills</h3>
      <p>Membina mindset positif, keyakinan diri dan kemahiran interpersonal yang relevan dengan nilai Islam.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="svc">
      <div class="svc-n">03 &mdash; TEKNOLOGI</div>
      <div class="svc-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Technical &amp; AI</h3>
      <p>Workshop hands-on penggunaan AI dalam kerja harian, automasi proses dan produktiviti digital.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="svc">
      <div class="svc-n">04 &mdash; SOSIAL</div>
      <div class="svc-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg></div>
      <h3>NGO &amp; Social Impact</h3>
      <p>Pembangunan kapasiti NGO &mdash; governance, fundraising, pengurusan program dan impak masyarakat.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="svc">
      <div class="svc-n">05 &mdash; DAKWAH</div>
      <div class="svc-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Dakwah Digital &amp; AI</h3>
      <p>Strategi dakwah melalui TikTok, YouTube, Facebook &amp; AI &mdash; menyampaikan Islam dengan cara relevan.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="svc svc-cta" onclick="window.location='hubungi.html'">
      <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      <span>Bincang keperluan<br>program anda</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="background:#fff;padding:64px 5%">
  <div style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto" class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-text-col">
      <div style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2.5px;color:#1a56db;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px">Kenali Saya</div>
      <div style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(28px,3.5vw,42px);font-weight:700;color:#0d1b3e;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-0.5px;margin-bottom:20px">Siapa <em style="font-style:italic;color:#1a56db">Bro Hafizi?</em></div>
      <p style="font-size:15px;color:#555;line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:16px">Bro Hafizi merupakan seorang <strong>pendakwah lapangan, AI Strategist dan Digital Dakwah Trainer</strong> yang aktif membantu organisasi, komuniti dan pendakwah memanfaatkan teknologi AI serta media digital untuk memperluaskan capaian dakwah secara lebih strategik dan berimpak.</p>
      <p style="font-size:15px;color:#555;line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:16px">Dengan gabungan pengalaman dalam dakwah lapangan, latihan profesional dan teknologi digital, beliau memberi fokus kepada pembangunan generasi pendakwah yang relevan dengan cabaran era moden.</p>
